{"tid":2455513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衞報告料指中國野生動物交易或是病毒傳播來源","createTime":"2021-03-21T07:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T09:08:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1e89b951a269b1854bcbe9110e38c7fffb63a42e","tid":2455513,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:36:24.000Z","msg":"世衞報告料指中國野生動物交易或是病毒傳播來源<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2743305/%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9E%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E6%96%99%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%87%8E%E7%94%9F%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%88%96%E6%98%AF%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2743305%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259E%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2587%258E%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%2592%25AD%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25BA%2590&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=ccbf414f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2743305/%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9E%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E6%96%99%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%87%8E%E7%94%9F%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%88%96%E6%98%AF%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90</a><br />\n<br />\n世衞專家組早前到武漢進行新冠病毒溯源工作，預料本周會公布報告。外電預料，報告會認定中國的野生動物交易可能是新型病毒的「傳播來源」。<br />\n<br />\n參與研究的美國衞生組織生態健康聯盟主席達扎克表示，武漢華南海鮮市場擺放的動物容易受新冠病毒感染，或是傳播渠道，把病毒從被視為主要來源的蝙蝠傳給人類，同沙士當年的傳播方式類似。<br />\n<br />\n專家組成員之一的澳洲傳染病專家德維爾表示，目前證據顯示，華南海鮮市場是新冠疫情得以擴大的地方，但不一定是病毒誕生地。有科學家指，在野生動物市場，兩個物種可能會被困在一起，令病毒在傳人類前得以適應和變強。一項研究發現，武漢的傳染病醫院最先治療的約100名患者中，約一半同華南海鮮市場有關。<br />\n<br />\n不過，報告未對病毒來源作最終定論，專家計劃在中國境內外做更多研究，了解新冠病毒如何形成，防止疫情日後回升或重臨。"},{"pid":"54ed43dd1e6c4c4661a688bcf1f39b47bab9e278","tid":2455513,"uid":394702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"留番戰埸上解釋<br />\n<br />\nTime will tell <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c62eeab840075667b778e87247e7ca1a07f729","tid":2455513,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072ba1059aa1ce7b284d7176675c40dc339c6ccf","tid":2455513,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce053007d7f1679d1aa33f077100704a9df5e9b4","tid":2455513,"uid":37596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"明明係支那人先係病毒傳播來源"},{"pid":"8fdb763460a516006554b7c4a50cd904395ba55b","tid":2455513,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"072ba1059aa1ce7b284d7176675c40dc339c6ccf","tid":2455513,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3065bc4a6afa1ae816967e47bb5eda34c4ca4ff2","tid":2455513,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"chi na virus"},{"pid":"fa32c66fddb37a96fa27798c9f6289adcc4b515f","tid":2455513,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"又話唔關支拿事？又話係天外來客？ 一時一樣  想點"},{"pid":"9e2ae40c053aecda2656e9e08e4e3a95ff65ad76","tid":2455513,"uid":40720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"美國重返who<br />\n就表達呢d立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傷透了中國同胞的感情"},{"pid":"5919995108c35847c5bceb6481f00d67ba5daa21","tid":2455513,"uid":34